---
// Services / How It Works Page — RankForward
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro'
import Row from '../components/ui/Row.astro'
import Col from '../components/ui/Col.astro'
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro'
import Hero from '../components/blocks/hero/BasicHeroCTA.astro'

const SEO = {
	title: 'RankForward | How It Works',
	description: 'How RankForward gets your business recommended by AI search engines. Our 3-step process built on Princeton University GEO research.'
}
---

<Layout title={SEO.title} description={SEO.description}>
	<Hero
		title="How RankForward Gets You Recommended by AI"
		text="Our process is built on peer-reviewed research from Princeton University (ACM KDD 2024) and real-world testing across hundreds of businesses."
		type="vertical"
		titleSpan="8"
	/>

	<!-- Step 1 -->
	<Section>
		<Row>
			<Col span="5">
				<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600 mb-4">Step 1</p>
				<h2>Submit Your URL</h2>
			</Col>
			<Col span="7" classes="self-end">
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">Enter your business website and we query ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Claude with 20+ prompts to see if they recommend you. You'll receive a detailed AI visibility score — your baseline — within 24 hours.</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">We test prompts like "Who is the best [your industry] in [your city]?" across every major AI engine. Most businesses score between 0 and 3 out of 10. This isn't a guess — it's a real measurement of how AI sees your business today.</p>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</Section>

	<!-- Step 2 -->
	<Section type="alt" decoration="all">
		<Row>
			<Col span="5">
				<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600 mb-4">Step 2</p>
				<h2>We Audit & Optimize</h2>
			</Col>
			<Col span="7" classes="self-end">
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">Our team analyzes your AI visibility across all engines and builds a custom GEO optimization roadmap. We identify exactly where you're invisible and what content changes will get you cited.</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">The Princeton GEO research identified 9 specific content optimization methods that increase AI citation rates. We apply the ones most relevant to your business:</p>
				<ul class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-2 ml-4">
					<li>&bull; Authoritative tone and language</li>
					<li>&bull; Credible citations and statistics</li>
					<li>&bull; Structured data and schema markup</li>
					<li>&bull; Third-party citation building</li>
					<li>&bull; Content restructuring for LLM readability</li>
				</ul>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</Section>

	<!-- Step 3 -->
	<Section>
		<Row>
			<Col span="5">
				<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600 mb-4">Step 3</p>
				<h2>You Get Recommended</h2>
			</Col>
			<Col span="7" classes="self-end">
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">We optimize your digital presence so AI engines cite your business when customers ask who to hire in your market. Monthly tracking shows your progress as AI engines start recognizing and recommending you.</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Every month, we re-run the full prompt battery, measure score changes, and report what's working. You'll see your AI visibility score climb as the optimizations compound over time.</p>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</Section>

	<!-- Princeton Research -->
	<Section type="alt" decoration="all">
		<Row>
			<Col span="12">
				<h2 class="text-center mb-8">Built on Princeton University Research</h2>
			</Col>
		</Row>
		<Row>
			<Col span="8" classes="mx-auto col-start-3">
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">Our methodology is grounded in the landmark GEO study published at ACM KDD 2024 by researchers at Princeton University, Georgia Tech, the Allen Institute, and IIT Delhi.</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">The research tested 9 content optimization methods across thousands of queries and found that systematic optimization can increase AI citation visibility by up to 40%. Key findings include:</p>
				<ul class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-2 ml-4 mb-8">
					<li>&bull; Content with statistics and cited sources gets cited significantly more often</li>
					<li>&bull; Authoritative language and expert quotations boost citation rates</li>
					<li>&bull; Structured, factual content outperforms generic marketing copy</li>
					<li>&bull; Third-party corroboration across multiple sources builds AI trust</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="text-center">
					<Button type="link" link="/#free-score" size="lg">Get Your Free AI Score &rarr;</Button>
				</div>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</Section>
</Layout>
